==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Loveliness
<hw>Love"li*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From <er>Lovely</er>.]</ety>
<def>The state or quality of being lovely.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>If there is such a native <qex>loveliness</qex> in the sex as to
make them victorious when in the wrong, how resistless their power when
they are on the side of truth!</q> <rj><qau>Spectator.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lovelock</ent>⟦br⟧
